arts.ttl: MLS fines Inter Miami's Lionel Messi for placing hand on New York City FC assistant coach's neck
arts.sum: Major League Soccer fined Inter Miami captain Lionel Messi an undisclosed amount on Tuesday for placing his hand on a New York City FC assistant coach’s neck. The league also fined Inter Miami forward Luis Suárez an undisclosed amount for violating the hands to the face/head/neck of an opponent policy in a separate incident in that match.

arts.ttl: Ollie Pearce double makes the difference for promotion hopefuls York
arts.sum: Tristan Abrahams equalised for the relegation-threatened Magpies just after the hour mark.
